OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FA motorist who hit a 12-year-old boy
OL,7,Fas he ran across a motorway has been
OL,8,Fcleared of dangerous driving after
OL,9,Ftelling a court he was a "broken man".
OL,11,FCallum Rycroft died from his injuries
OL,12,Fafter being hit by a car driven by
OL,13,FShahid Ilyas, 48, as he crossed the
OL,14,FM62 in West Yorkshire on 5 August.
OL,16,FProsecutors told Bradford Crown Court
OL,17,FShahid Ilyas, 48, was not responsible
OL,18,Ffor Callum's death.
