OL,3,CMotorist who hit 12-year-old on M62
OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FBut they claimed he had driven
OL,7,Fdangerously after the incident because
OL,8,Fhe allegedly failed to stop as soon as
OL,9,Fhe safely could, despite "massive
OL,10,Fdamage" to his windscreen.
OL,12,FHowever, a jury took around two hours
OL,13,Fto clear Mr Ilyas of dangerous driving.
OL,15,FEarlier Mr Ilyas had told the jury: "I
OL,16,Fwas driving along at a normal speed,
OL,17,Fminding my own business and suddenly
OL,18,Fthere was a loud bang and the
OL,19,Fwindscreen bowed in."
