OL,3,CMotorist who hit 12-year-old on M62
OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FHe said: "I was in shock and I was
OL,7,Ftraumatised. I didn't know if I was
OL,8,Fdead or alive."
OL,10,FMr Ilyas told the court how he
OL,11,Fsqueezed his leg to see if he could
OL,12,Ffeel anything, because he did not know
OL,13,Fif what was happening to him was real
OL,14,For a nightmare.
OL,16,FHe told the jury: "I know I look
OL,17,Fnormal on the outside but inside I'm a
OL,18,Fbroken man.
