OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F368A1728858463
OL,3,CMotorist who hit 12-year-old on M62
OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FHe said: "My life has been turned
OL,7,Fupside down because of this accident
OL,8,Fand it was not my fault.
OL,10,F"I did not create this accident. I did
OL,11,Fnot commit a crime and I've been
OL,12,Ftreated like a criminal."
OL,14,FMr Ilyas described how, immediately
OL,15,Fafter the collision, he put on his
OL,16,Fhazard lights and pulled the Toyota to
OL,17,Fthe left hand side of the motorway and
OL,18,Fgot out of the vehicle.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUtD@YO]
