OL,3,CMotorist who hit 12-year-old on M62
OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FBut he said he realised there was no
OL,7,Fhard shoulder and he was in a live
OL,8,Flane with traffic "flying past".
OL,10,FThe defendant said: "I was thinking to
OL,11,Fgo to a service station and that's
OL,12,Fwhat I did, and that's what it says in
OL,13,Fthe Highway Code."
OL,15,FProsecutors have told the jury the
OL,16,Fcase against Ilyas is that he drove on
OL,17,Fafter the collision for about two-a-
OL,18,Fhalf miles, ignoring at least two
OL,19,Fclear places to stop, before pulling
OL,20,Finto an Esso service station on
OL,21,FWhitehall Lane, in Bradford.
