OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FMr Ilyas told the jury: "In a state of
OL,7,Fshock and a state of trauma I went to
OL,8,Fgo to a service station.
OL,10,F"I do not remember looking for a
OL,11,Flayby, or bus stop or people's
OL,12,Fdriveway to stop."
OL,14,FAsked about the state of his shattered
OL,15,Fwindscreen, Ilyas said: "I had enough
OL,16,Fview to see where I was going."
OL,18,FWhen he reached a garage and admitted
OL,19,Fhe told workers he had hit an animal.
