OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FHe said he only realised what had
OL,7,Factually happened the next day when
OL,8,Fstories about Callum's death appeared
OL,9,Fin the news.
OL,11,FThe court has heard how Ilyas then
OL,12,Fcontacted a solicitor for advice, who
OL,13,Frang the police on his behalf.
OL,15,FThe defendant said he has not been
OL,16,Fable to drive since the incident due
OL,17,Fto the trauma.
