OL,6,FThe jury of six men and six women was
OL,7,Fshown footage of the fatal collision
OL,8,Fon the motorway and some of the build-
OL,9,Fup to the incident.
OL,11,FMichael Smith, prosecuting, told the
OL,12,Fcourt that the incident happened after
OL,13,FCallum's father, Matthew Rycroft, was
OL,14,Fdriving drunk on the motorway and
OL,15,Foverturned his Audi Q5 on the slip
OL,16,Froad to Hartshead Moor services, near
OL,17,FHuddersfield.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
