OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F368A1728858463
OL,3,CMotorist who hit 12-year-old on M62
OL,4,Ccleared of dangerous driving
OL,6,FRycroft and Callum left the vehicle
OL,7,Fand were seen on CCTV, shown to the
OL,8,Fcourt on Friday, walking along the
OL,9,Fbusy M62 in the dark before crossing
OL,10,Finto the central reservation.
OL,12,FAt one point, Rycroft was seen falling
OL,13,Fover and being helped up by Callum,
OL,14,Fthe court heard.
OL,16,FRycroft then crossed back over to the
OL,17,Fhard shoulder and was followed by
OL,18,FCallum, who ran directly into the path
OL,19,Fof Ilyas's Toyota.
