OL,6,FRycroft made it to the other side and
OL,7,Fcarried on without looking back for
OL,8,Fhis son, the court heard.
OL,10,FThe jury was told that Rycroft
OL,11,Fadmitted his son's manslaughter in a
OL,12,Fseparate prosecution and has been
OL,13,Fdealt with by the courts.
